兰本地原先由2014年从CD Projekt分离出的发行公司CDP负责分销，但是在2020年4月该公司宣布倒闭，《赛博朋克2077》在波兰的销售由Cenega接手。<ref>[https://www.pcgamer.com/cyberpunk-2077s-former-polish-distributor-has-filed-for-bankruptcy/ Cyberpunk 2077's former Polish distributor has filed for bankruptcy] {{Wayback|url=https://www.pcgamer.com/cyberpunk-2077s-former-polish-distributor-has-filed-for-bankruptcy/ |date=20200621183120 }}.PCGamer.2020-04-22.[2020-06-26].</ref>

